[00:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
AUDIO: 'to create its own scaffold while solving tasks. So, instead of only learning how to write the answer, it also learns how to structure the process that gets to the answer. That means things like how it plans, how it retries, how it handles mistakes, how it'

