VISUAL: DeepReinforce website showing a diagram titled "Jointly optimized" illustrating Ornith's task scaffold and reward feedback loop.
AUDIO: 'uses tools, how it checks files, and how it runs tests. This matters a lot for coding agents. Because with coding models, the model itself is only one part of the experience.'

[01:21] [scene:ui]
VISUAL: DeepReinforce website showing the "Jointly optimized" diagram.
AUDIO: 'The harness matters a lot. The tool calling matters. The way it reads files matters. The way it recovers from errors matters. You can have a very strong model, but if the agent loop is bad, it will feel terrible. And, you can have a smaller'

[01:33] [scene:talk]
VISUAL: 
