[01:45] [scene:ui]
VISUAL: DeepReinforce website highlighting text about defending against reward hacking.
AUDIO: 'tasks, there is always a risk that it learns how to game the benchmark instead of actually solving the task. For example, it might read visible tests and hardcode the output. It might touch the file that the checker wants. It might copy something from the environment.'

[01:57] [scene:ui]
